title: OPTPC - Saleha Abdou
transcript:
Majestic

empowered, beautiful and serene
I own my truth
Confident is my last name
Look into my eyes of flame
Look into the windows of my soul
you'll see the fiery phoenix that was once tamed Once upon a time it escaped its cage
Breaking the chains of limitation
It flew and lit the night sky
Starting a spark for other caged birds to see That hope is never lost and magic can never be tamed My legacy continues
Look into me now
empowered, beautiful and serene
